=== Velometer Bicycle Counter ===

http://velometer.tumblr.com/

This software controls the Velometer Bicycle Counter.  The counter features:

* 4 digit LED matrix display
* Pressure sensor for detecting bicycles
* Real-time clock automatically resets counter each day
* Bicycle counter value saved to EEPROM every 5 minutes

GNU LGPL licensed


=== Hardware ===

* Arduino Uno microcontroller board
* Freescale MPX4250 differential pressure sensor
* Maxim MAX6953 matrix LED display driver
* Maxim DS1337 real-time clock


=== Dependencies ===

* DS1337 RTC library sourced from Mosquino project
  https://code.google.com/p/mosquino/
  http://arduino.cc/forum/index.php?topic=38077.0

* Some code portions adapted from:

  * Pressure sensor smoothing (running average)
    http://arduino.cc/en/Tutorial/Smoothing

  * EEPROM read/write
    http://playground.arduino.cc/Code/EEPROMWriteAnything

